column3: yɛ aso ma mo nkotoserɛ: Gye me do wɔ wo nokwardzi na wo tsenenee mu."

column2: "Na mma mmfa w'akowaa nnkɔ atsɛmbu mu; Na ɔwo w'enyim ɔtseasefo biara rinndzi bem."
"Na ɔtamfo no ahaw me kra; Ɔabɔ mo nkwa ahwe famu: Ɔama matsena sum mbeambea do dɛ hɔn a woewu akyɛr."
"Dɛm ntsi mo sunsum atɔ bitsi wɔ mo mu; M'akoma ayɛ ankonam wɔ mo mu."
"Mekaa tsetse nda no; Modwendwen wo ndzeyɛe nyinara ho: Mususu wo nsaano edwuma ho."
"Mema me nsa do kyerɛ wo: Wo ho sukɔm dze me kra

column3: yɛ ntsɛm gye me do; m'ahom repa: Mma nnyi w'enyim nnhuntsa me ae; Bɛyɛ na mayɛ dɛ hɔn a wosian kɔ adakamona mu no."

column2: "Ma mentse w'adɔyɛ nka anapa; Na ɔwo na motwer wo: Ma munhu akwan a ɔsɛ dɛ menantsew do; Na ɔwo na mema me kra do ma wo."

column4: gye me fi m'atamfo nsa: Muguan toa wo dɛ fa me huntsa."

column2: "Kyerɛkyerɛ me ma menyɛ wo pɛ; na ɔwo nye me Nyankopɔn: Ma wo sunsum akwankyerɛ pa no ngya me mfa tsenenee asaase do."

column3: gye me nkwa wɔ wo dzin ntsi: Yi me kra fi ɔfona mu wɔ wo ndzeyɛtsenenee mu."

column2: "Na twa m'atamfo gu wɔ w'adɔyɛ mu
column3: Na sɛɛ hɔn a wohiahia me kra ho nyinara; Osiandɛ meyɛ w'akowaa."
